  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[On Play] By returning the top card of your security stack
    to the hand, you may place 1 yellow card with the [Vaccine] trait from your hand
    at the bottom of your security stack. [Your Turn] When a card is added to your
    security stack, by suspending this Tamer, gain 1 memory.'
